textBox.richText: Jyang to do list and known bugs

A list that is configuration data must have a key statement. If the parent list is a configuration data, so the list is also a configuration data. Theses modules : ietf-netconf-partial-lock, ipfixpsamp, system, and test of the netconfcentral module page (http://www.netconfcentral.com/modulelist) have a list with no key.
